🌍 Travel Planning CLI
A command-line interface (CLI) application to manage users, trips, and activities. This tool helps users plan and organize travel itineraries efficiently using Python and SQLAlchemy.

✨ Features
✅ User Management – Add, view, and delete users.
✅ Trip Management – Create, view, and delete trips associated with users.
✅ Activity Management – Assign activities to trips and remove them as needed.
✅ Interactive Menu – Navigate smoothly with an easy-to-use CLI interface.
✅ Data Persistence – Uses SQLite to store all user, trip, and activity data.

🛠 Technologies Used
Python 3.8+ – Programming language
SQLAlchemy – ORM for database management
SQLite – Database for storing user, trip, and activity data
Alembic – Database migrations
Faker – Generate fake user data for testing
